    Note: AST Diffing Tests
    Display message "\nAST Diffing Tests:"
    test_diff_ast_identical()
    test_diff_ast_type_difference()
    test_diff_ast_children_count()
    
    Note: AST Merging Tests
    Display message "\nAST Merging Tests:"
