    Display message "Total Tests: " plus test_count
    Display message "Tests Passed: " plus passed_count
    Display message "Tests Failed: " plus failed_count
    
    If failed_count is equal to 0:
        Display message "✅ ALL AST MANIPULATION TESTS PASSED!"
    Otherwise:
        Display message "❌ " plus failed_count plus " TESTS FAILED"
    
    Display message "=" repeated 70

Note: Execute the test suite
run_all_ast_manipulation_tests()